
Regular podcast interviews and commented-upon powerpoint presentations, with leaders of the digital media industry.

URL = http://www.insidedigitalmedia.com/

"Inside Digital Media, Inc. is a place where you can see and hear interviews with thought leaders in the Digital Media industries. There are two formats. First, is audio-only, which is much like talk radio over the Internet. To hear the interview streams at your computer you will need the RealPlayer. If instead you choose to download the interviews, you may burn them to blank CDs or transfer them to portable devices like the iPod. For example, with the dot-MP3 downloads you can hear our interviews in your car. The second type of interview is a synchronized PowerPoint presentation with voice-over of the conversation between me and my guest. The first time you watch a show you will be asked to authorize a thin WebEx client to install automatically on your computer thereby enabling you to watch the programs."

